name: breakfast for dinner
description:
Puppet self portrait face swap w/ dialogue. 

Puppet was created in 2017 with a silicone copy of the artist's face, their child's hair for the eyebrows, grandma's cancer wig for the hair, baboon taxidermy eyes, and dentures sourced from Ebay.  

"what did you have for breakfast today?"
"I eat paint chips, and I eat bicycle spokes, and gasoline. What did you have"
"Well, I had some grape nuts and corn chips."
"I prefer bicycle spokes and gasoline."
